General.Name: Penneo AS
General.Description: Penneo A/S, a software-as-a-service company, provides an eco-system of automation solutions that digitizes companies' workflows of customers onboarding, and signing and managing documents. It offers software for the audit and accounting industry. The company's solutions include Penneo Sign for digital signing, workflow automation, and data collection; and Penneo KYC to automate the client onboarding process. The company serves customers in audit and accounting, finance and banking, real estate, legal, and general administration industries. It operates in Denmark, Sweden, Norway, Belgium, Finland, Germany, and internationally. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Copenhagen, Denmark.
